      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is absolutely crucial that you do not attempt to switch from warfarin to herbal remedies like garlic or green smoothies without consulting your doctor. Warfarin is a powerful prescription medication that requires precise monitoring to prevent dangerous clotting or bleeding events. Any change in your diet or introduction of supplements can drastically alter how your body processes the medication, putting you at serious risk. Please discuss your concerns about testing and diet with your healthcare provider immediately to find a safe management plan.",
