      "content": "i'm just so tired of the doctor telling me no every time i bring something up. it feels like they just want to keep me on the pills for money. if i was going to try and taper off the warfarin on my own, how much garlic should i be taking daily to make sure my blood stays thin enough so i dont get a clot while i transition?",
